value.original: Default Logic
Default value hierarchy, separated by ;

The defaults are evaluated in the order of definition, the first not null value becomes the default value of the column. The values are separated by comma or semicolon. a) Literals:. 'Text' or 123 b) Variables - in format @Variable@ - Login e.g. #Date, #AD_Org_ID, #AD_Client_ID - Accounting Schema: e.g. $C_AcctSchema_ID, $C_Calendar_ID - Global defaults: e.g. DateFormat - Window values (all Picks, CheckBoxes, RadioButtons, and DateDoc/DateAcct) c) SQL code with the tag: @SQL=SELECT something AS DefaultValue FROM ... The SQL statement can contain variables. There can be no other value other than the SQL statement. The default is only evaluated, if no user preference is defined. Default definitions are ignored for record columns as Key, Parent, Client as well as Buttons.

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

row.value: 有两种方法在系统内使数据失效: 一是删除数据, 另一个是取消激活数据. 一个取消激活的记录无法被选择,但是报告时可用.有两个原因使用取消激活而不删除记录:(1) 系统因为审计原因需求记录(2) 别的记录引用当前的记录. 例, 如果有一些莫个关于业务伙伴的发票存在,你就不能删除这个业务伙伴. 你取消激活这个业务伙伴以防止这个记录被未来的入口使用..

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. value.original:
The SO Sub Type indicates the type of sales order this document refers to. This field only appears when the Document Base Type is Sales Order. The selection made here will determine which documents will be generated when an order is processed and which documents must be generated manually or in batches.
The following outlines this process.
SO Sub Type of Standard Order will generate just the Order document when the order is processed.
The Delivery Note, Invoice and Receipt must be generated via other processes.
SO Sub Type of Warehouse Order will generate the Order and Delivery Note.
The Invoice and Receipt must be generated via other processes.
SO Sub Type of Credit Order will generate the Order, Delivery Note and Invoice.
The Reciept must be generated via other processes.
SO Sub Type of POS (Point of Sale) will generate all document

row.value: 这子类类型指出这个文档引用的销售订单类型.文档基类型是销售订单时这个字段单独的显示.该选择使订单处理时,要产生哪个文档和哪些要手工地或成批产生.(以下是处理概要): 子类类型是标准订单仅产生这(订单)文档并处理,而交货单、发票和收据要通过其它处理产生. 子类类型是仓库订单产生(订单和交货单),而发票和收据要通过其它处理产生. 子类类型是贷方订单产生(订单、交货单和发票),而收据要通过其它处理产生. 子类类型是POS(销售点)可能产生全部的文档。

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

value.original: Default Logic
Default value hierarchy, separated by ;

The defaults are evaluated in the order of definition, the first not null value becomes the default value of the column. The values are separated by comma or semicolon. a) Literals:. 'Text' or 123 b) Variables - in format @Variable@ - Login e.g. #Date, #AD_Org_ID, #AD_Client_ID - Accounting Schema: e.g. $C_AcctSchema_ID, $C_Calendar_ID - Global defaults: e.g. DateFormat - Window values (all Picks, CheckBoxes, RadioButtons, and DateDoc/DateAcct) c) SQL code with the tag: @SQL=SELECT something AS DefaultValue FROM ... The SQL statement can contain variables. There can be no other value other than the SQL statement. The default is only evaluated, if no user preference is defined. Default definitions are ignored for record columns as Key, Parent, Client as well as Buttons.

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

value.original: Client for this installation.
A Client is a company or a legal entity. You cannot share data between Clients.

row.value: 客户是公司或法人.你不能在客户间共享数据。

value.original: Organizational entity within client
An organization is a unit of your client or legal entity - examples are store, department. You can share data between organizations.

row.value: 分公司/组织是指客户或法人中的一个，比如商店，部门。你可以在分公司/组织之间共享数据。

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

row.value: 有两种方法在系统内使数据失效: 一是删除数据, 另一个是取消激活数据. 一个取消激活的记录无法被选择,但是报告时可用.有两个原因使用取消激活而不删除记录:(1) 系统因为审计原因需求记录(2) 别的记录引用当前的记录. 例, 如果有一些莫个关于业务伙伴的发票存在,你就不能删除这个业务伙伴. 你取消激活这个业务伙伴以防止这个记录被未来的入口使用..

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. value.original: Default Logic
Default value hierarchy, separated by ;

The defaults are evaluated in the order of definition, the first not null value becomes the default value of the column. The values are separated by comma or semicolon. a) Literals:. 'Text' or 123 b) Variables - in format @Variable@ - Login e.g. #Date, #AD_Org_ID, #AD_Client_ID - Accounting Schema: e.g. $C_AcctSchema_ID, $C_Calendar_ID - Global defaults: e.g. DateFormat - Window values (all Picks, CheckBoxes, RadioButtons, and DateDoc/DateAcct) c) SQL code with the tag: @SQL=SELECT something AS DefaultValue FROM ... The SQL statement can contain variables. There can be no other value other than the SQL statement. The default is only evaluated, if no user preference is defined. Default definitions are ignored for record columns as Key, Parent, Client as well as Buttons.

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

value.original: Default Logic
Default value hierarchy, separated by ;

The defaults are evaluated in the order of definition, the first not null value becomes the default value of the column. The values are separated by comma or semicolon. a) Literals:. 'Text' or 123 b) Variables - in format @Variable@ - Login e.g. #Date, #AD_Org_ID, #AD_Client_ID - Accounting Schema: e.g. $C_AcctSchema_ID, $C_Calendar_ID - Global defaults: e.g. DateFormat - Window values (all Picks, CheckBoxes, RadioButtons, and DateDoc/DateAcct) c) SQL code with the tag: @SQL=SELECT something AS DefaultValue FROM ... The SQL statement can contain variables. There can be no other value other than the SQL statement. The default is only evaluated, if no user preference is defined. Default definitions are ignored for record columns as Key, Parent, Client as well as Buttons.

A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

The relative weight allows you to adjust the project cycle report based on probabilities. For example, if you have a 1:10 chance in closing a contract when it is in the prospect stage and a 1:2 chance when it is in the contract stage, you may put a weight of 0.1 and 0.5 on those steps. value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

row.value: 有两种方法在系统内使数据失效: 一是删除数据, 另一个是取消激活数据. 一个取消激活的记录无法被选择,但是报告时可用.有两个原因使用取消激活而不删除记录:(1) 系统因为审计原因需求记录(2) 别的记录引用当前的记录. 例, 如果有一些莫个关于业务伙伴的发票存在,你就不能删除这个业务伙伴. 你取消激活这个业务伙伴以防止这个记录被未来的入口使用..

A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: The Verify BOM Structure checks the elements and steps which comprise a Bill of Materials.

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

row.value: 有两种方法在系统内使数据失效: 一是删除数据, 另一个是取消激活数据. 一个取消激活的记录无法被选择,但是报告时可用.有两个原因使用取消激活而不删除记录:(1) 系统因为审计原因需求记录(2) 别的记录引用当前的记录. 例, 如果有一些莫个关于业务伙伴的发票存在,你就不能删除这个业务伙伴. 你取消激活这个业务伙伴以防止这个记录被未来的入口使用..

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

row.value: 有两种方法在系统内使数据失效: 一是删除数据, 另一个是取消激活数据. 一个取消激活的记录无法被选择,但是报告时可用.有两个原因使用取消激活而不删除记录:(1) 系统因为审计原因需求记录(2) 别的记录引用当前的记录. 例, 如果有一些莫个关于业务伙伴的发票存在,你就不能删除这个业务伙伴. 你取消激活这个业务伙伴以防止这个记录被未来的入口使用..

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

row.value: 有两种方法在系统内使数据失效: 一是删除数据, 另一个是取消激活数据. 一个取消激活的记录无法被选择,但是报告时可用.有两个原因使用取消激活而不删除记录:(1) 系统因为审计原因需求记录(2) 别的记录引用当前的记录. 例, 如果有一些莫个关于业务伙伴的发票存在,你就不能删除这个业务伙伴. 你取消激活这个业务伙伴以防止这个记录被未来的入口使用..

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. value.original: Relative Weight
Relative weight of this step (0 = ignored)

The relative weight allows you to adjust the project cycle report based on probabilities. For example, if you have a 1:10 chance in closing a contract when it is in the prospect stage and a 1:2 chance when it is in the contract stage, you may put a weight of 0.1 and 0.5 on those steps. This allows sales funnels or measures of completion of your project.

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

row.value: 有两种方法在系统内使数据失效: 一是删除数据, 另一个是取消激活数据. 一个取消激活的记录无法被选择,但是报告时可用.有两个原因使用取消激活而不删除记录:(1) 系统因为审计原因需求记录(2) 别的记录引用当前的记录. 例, 如果有一些莫个关于业务伙伴的发票存在,你就不能删除这个业务伙伴. 你取消激活这个业务伙伴以防止这个记录被未来的入口使用..

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

value.original: The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

row.value: 有两种方法在系统内使数据失效: 一是删除数据, 另一个是取消激活数据. 一个取消激活的记录无法被选择,但是报告时可用.有两个原因使用取消激活而不删除记录:(1) 系统因为审计原因需求记录(2) 别的记录引用当前的记录. 例, 如果有一些莫个关于业务伙伴的发票存在,你就不能删除这个业务伙伴. 你取消激活这个业务伙伴以防止这个记录被未来的入口使用..

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

row.value: 有两种方法在系统内使数据失效: 一是删除数据, 另一个是取消激活数据. 一个取消激活的记录无法被选择,但是报告时可用.有两个原因使用取消激活而不删除记录:(1) 系统因为审计原因需求记录(2) 别的记录引用当前的记录. 例, 如果有一些莫个关于业务伙伴的发票存在,你就不能删除这个业务伙伴. 你取消激活这个业务伙伴以防止这个记录被未来的入口使用..

A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports.There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records:(1) The system requires the record for audit purposes.(2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.

row.value: 有两种方法在系统内使数据失效: 一是删除数据, 另一个是取消激活数据. 一个取消激活的记录无法被选择,但是报告时可用.有两个原因使用取消激活而不删除记录:(1) 系统因为审计原因需求记录(2) 别的记录引用当前的记录. 例, 如果有一些莫个关于业务伙伴的发票存在,你就不能删除这个业务伙伴. 你取消激活这个业务伙伴以防止这个记录被未来的入口使用..

value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. value.original: Document No
Document sequence number of the document

The document number is usually automatically generated by the system and determined by the document type of the document. If the document is not saved, the preliminary number is displayed in "<>".If the document type of your document has no automatic document sequence defined, the field is empty if you create a new document. This is for documents which usually have an external number (like vendor invoice). If you leave the field empty, the system will generate a document number for you. The document sequence used for this fallback number is defined in the "Maintain Sequence" window with the name "DocumentNo_<TableName>", where TableName is the actual name of the table (e.g. C_Order).

row.value: 记录号由系统根据记录类型自动生成。如果没有保存记录，前一记录的记录号将在（）中显示。如果新建一个无法自动排序的记录，记录号处将留空。此种记录通常包含一个外部记录编号（如卖方发票）。如果在此处不填写任何信息，系统在保存时会自动生成一个号码。用于反馈的这个记录序列号是由窗体"Maintain Sequence" （窗体名："DocumentNo_( TableName )"）所决定，此处TableName是实际的表格名称，如C_Order。

E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.
